            <h1>How to Warm Up a New TikTok Account<br><span>(So You Don't Get Zero Views)</span></h1>
            <p class="hsub">The exact process to launch a fresh account so the algorithm treats you like a real human, not a bot it needs to suppress.</p>
            
            <div class="hmeta">
                <span>Tan Ağırkaya</span>
                <span style="color:var(--border-color)">•</span>
                <span>6 min read</span>
                <span style="color:var(--border-color)">•</span>
